;Bit Definitions for state flag

STATE_IDLE          EQU     0x00
STATE_LAUNCH        EQU     0x04
STATE_FLIGHT        EQU     0x08
STATE_GROUNDED      EQU     0x0C
STATE_BEACON        EQU     0x10
STATE_SLEEP         EQU     0x14
STATE_TEST          EQU     0x18
STATE_MAX           EQU     STATE_TEST
